Interface PropertyAccessor<D extends BioPAXElement,R>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataPropertyEditor<D,R>, PropertyEditor<D,R>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPropertyEditor, DecoratingPropertyAccessor, EnumeratedPropertyEditor, FilteredPropertyAccessor, ObjectPropertyEditor, PathAccessor, PrimitivePropertyEditor, PropertyAccessorAdapter, SimplePropertyAccessor, StringPropertyEditor, TransitivePropertyAccessor, UnionPropertyAccessor

    public interface PropertyAccessor<D extends BioPAXElement,R>
    Allows generic access to the properties or a path of properties from a bean.
